            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20Satan's%20motto%3A%20%22a%20different%20Jesus%20.%20.%20.%20a%20different%20Spirit%20.%20.%20.%20a%20different%20gospel%22!%20He%20disguises%20himself%20as%20%22an%20angel%20of%20light%22%20(2%20Corinthians%2011%3A14)%2C%20putting%20on%20a%20religious%20and%20holy%20front%20while%20attempting%20to%20deceive%20us.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPaul%20warned%20the%20Corinthians%20about%20the%20subtlety%20of%20the%20one%20who%20came%20to%20Eve%20with%20a%20slight%20twist%20to%20the%20commandment%20of%20God.%20Satan%20tries%20to%20take%20the%20focus%20off%20the%20cross%2C%20the%20person%20of%20Jesus%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20sin%2C%20the%20need%20for%20repentance%2C%20and%20the%20certainty%20of%20hell.%20He%20tries%20instead%20to%20bring%20us%20another%20gospel%2C%20one%20that%20focuses%20on%20man's%20goodness%2C%20the%20equality%20of%20all%20religions%2C%20the%20nonessentiality%20of%20the%20blood%20of%20Jesus%2C%20and%20the%20ridiculousness%20of%20an%20eternal%20hell.%20All%20these%20variations%20of%20the%20Gospel%20sound%20good%20to%20the%20natural%20mind%2C%20but%20Paul%20recognized%20them%20as%20Satan's%20disguise%20for%20the%20true%20Gospel%20(2%20Corinthians%2011%3A13-15).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIsaiah%20said%2C%20%22Destruction%20is%20certain%20for%20those%20who%20say%20that%20evil%20is%20good%20and%20good%20is%20evil%3B%20that%20dark%20is%20light%20and%20light%20is%20dark%3B%20that%20bitter%20is%20sweet%20and%20sweet%20is%20bitter%22%20(Isaiah%205%3A20).%20Satan%20can%20call%20it%20what%20he%20likes%2C%20but%20sin%20is%20sin%2C%20God%20is%20pure%2C%20and%20hell%20is%20forever!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStay%20simple%20in%20your%20sincere%20and%20pure%20devotion%20to%20the%20real%20Jesus.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
