            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%203%3A1-5%3A30%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJudgment%20against%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Lord%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewill%20take%20away%20from%20Jerusalem%20and%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eeverything%20they%20depend%20on%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eevery%20bit%20of%20bread%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20every%20drop%20of%20water%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3Eall%20their%20heroes%20and%20soldiers%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ejudges%20and%20prophets%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efortune-tellers%20and%20elders%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3Earmy%20officers%20and%20high%20officials%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eadvisers%2C%20skilled%20sorcerers%2C%20and%20astrologers.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20make%20boys%20their%20leaders%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20toddlers%20their%20rulers.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EPeople%20will%20oppress%20each%20other%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eman%20against%20man%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eneighbor%20against%20neighbor.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYoung%20people%20will%20insult%20their%20elders%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20vulgar%20people%20will%20sneer%20at%20the%20honorable.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20those%20days%20a%20man%20will%20say%20to%20his%20brother%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BSince%20you%20have%20a%20coat%2C%20you%20be%20our%20leader!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ETake%20charge%20of%20this%20heap%20of%20ruins!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20he%20will%20reply%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BNo!%20I%20can%26%23x2019%3Bt%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20have%20any%20extra%20food%20or%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20put%20me%20in%20charge!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20Jerusalem%20will%20stumble%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20Judah%20will%20fall%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ebecause%20they%20speak%20out%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20refuse%20to%20obey%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20provoke%20him%20to%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20very%20look%20on%20their%20faces%20gives%20them%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20display%20their%20sin%20like%20the%20people%20of%20Sodom%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20even%20try%20to%20hide%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20are%20doomed!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20have%20brought%20destruction%20upon%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3ETell%20the%20godly%20that%20all%20will%20be%20well%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20will%20enjoy%20the%20rich%20reward%20they%20have%20earned!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_11%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20wicked%20are%20doomed%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20they%20will%20get%20exactly%20what%20they%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_3_12%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%223%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EChildish%20leaders%20oppress%20my%20people%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20women%20rule%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EO%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20people%2C%20your%20leaders%20mislead%20you%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C